 2017 for Det Kgl. Bibliotek | url=http://www5.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/kb/aarsrapport/KB-Arsrapport-2017.pdf | date=5 March 2018 | publisher=Det Kgl. Bibliotek | accessdate=5 April 2020 | language=da }}</ref>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0000850301</span>1.45 million<ref name=Aarsberetning2017/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_02249892000</span>{{nobr|523.8 million [[Danish krone|DKK]]}}<ref name=Aarsberetning2017/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_00492</span>800+<ref>{{cite web|title=Job og karriere | url=https://www.kb.dk/om-os/job-og-karriere | publisher=Det Kgl. Bibliotek | accessdate=5 April 2020 | language=da }}</ref>\n|-\n| 8\n| [[National Diet Library]]\n| {{flag|Japan}}  \n| [[Tokyo]] and [[Kyoto]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0041900000</span>41.9&nbsp;million<ref name=\"ndl\">{{cite web|year=2017|url=http://ndl.go.jp/en/aboutus/outline/numerically.html|title=National Diet Library Statistics|accessdate=2017-04-06}}</ref>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0000654000</span>654,000<ref name=\"ndl\"/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_07128927000</span>{{nobr|[[Japanese yen|\u00a5]]21.8 billion}}<ref name=\"ndl\"/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_00908</span>908<ref name=\"ndl\"/>\n|-\n| 9\n| [[Biblioth\u00e8que nationale de France]]\n| {{flag|France}}  \n| [[Paris]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0040000000</span>40&nbsp;million<ref>{{cite web|date=8 March 2010 |url=http://www.bnf.fr/en/bnf/presentation_space/a.abc_of_the_collections.html#SHDC__Attribute_BlocArticle7BnF |title=BnF - ABC of the collections: N for Numerous |accessdate=2010-07-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65oi4Cksu?url=http://www.bnf.fr/en/bnf/presentation_space/a.abc_of_the_collections.html |archivedate=29 February 2012 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0001300000</span>1.3&nbsp;million<ref>{{cite web|date=14 October 2009 |url=http://www.bnf.fr/fr/la_bnf/bnf_en_chiffres/s.chiffres_publics.html?first_Art=non |title=BnF - La BnF en chiffres - 