ninka\">{{cite web|date=1 January 2019|url=https://www.rsl.ru/photo/!_ORS/6-NOVOSTI/2019/report2018/RGB_report_2018_low.pdf|title=\u0413\u043e\u0434\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0439 \u043e\u0442\u0447\u0435\u0442 \u0420\u0413\u0411 2018 (\u043f\u043e \u0441\u043e\u0441\u0442\u043e\u044f\u043d\u0438\u044e \u043d\u0430 01.01.2019)|accessdate=2019-06-17}}</ref>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0001170000</span>0.964&nbsp;million<ref name=\"leninka\"/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_01640000000</span>{{nobr|2.4 billion [[Russian ruble|RUB]]}}<ref name=\"leninka\"/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_01972</span>1,618<ref name=\"leninka\"/>\n|-\n| 7\n| [[Royal Danish Library]]\n| {{flag|Denmark}}  \n| [[Copenhagen]] and [[Aarhus]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0035400000</span>42.5&nbsp;million (physical items, excl. digital)<ref name=Aarsberetning2017>{{cite web|title=\u00c5rsrapport 2017 for Det Kgl. Bibliotek | url=http://www5.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/kb/aarsrapport/KB-Arsrapport-2017.pdf | date=5 March 2018 | publisher=Det Kgl. Bibliotek | accessdate=5 April 2020 | language=da }}</ref>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0000850301</span>1.45 million<ref name=Aarsberetning2017/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_02249892000</span>{{nobr|523.8 million [[Danish krone|DKK]]}}<ref name=Aarsberetning2017/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_00492</span>800+<ref>{{cite web|title=Job og karriere | url=https://www.kb.dk/om-os/job-og-karriere | publisher=Det Kgl. Bibliotek | accessdate=5 April 2020 | language=da }}</ref>\n|-\n| 8\n| [[National Diet Library]]\n| {{flag|Japan}}  \n| [[Tokyo]] and [[Kyoto]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0041900000</span>41.9&nbsp;million<ref name=\"ndl\">{{cite web|year=2017|url=http://ndl.go.jp/en/aboutus/outline/numerically.html|title=National Diet Library Statistics|accessdate=2017-04-06}}</ref>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_0000654000</span>654,000<ref name=\"ndl\"/>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">_07128927000</span>{{nobr|[[Japanese yen|\u00a